about.summary: Routines to model ocean carbonate system thermodynamics.

name: mocsy
raw_recipe:
{% set version = "2.3.2" %}

package:
  name: mocsy
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  fn: mocsy-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  url: https://github.com/jamesorr/mocsy/archive/v{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: acc8793071d36df62efdd2cd1beed7f76f69505eee1201d12d147a1a18a2b46d

build:
  number: 0
  skip: True  # [win or osx or py2k]

requirements:
  build:
    - python
    - setuptools
    - numpy x.x
    - gcc  # [not win]
  run:
    - python
    - numpy x.x
    - libgcc  # [linux]

test:
  imports:
    - mocsy

about:
  home: https://github.com/jamesorr/mocsy.git
  license: MIT
  summary: 'Routines to model ocean carbonate system thermodynamics.'

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - ocefpaf
